    M

    main - 程序包 main
     
    main(String[]) - 类中的静态方法 main.MainApplication
    The main method that serves as the entry point for the application.
    MainApplication - main中的类
    Main application entry point for the Recipe Management System.
    MainApplication() - 类的构造器 main.MainApplication
     
    model - 程序包 model
     
    Model - model中的类
    Model class serves as the main business logic layer for the recipe management application.
    Model() - 类的构造器 model.Model
    Default constructor for Model class.
    ModelMethod - model中的接口
    Interface defining the contract for model operations in the recipe management system.
